WEBVTT

02:11.190 --> 02:12.750
I know that after you woke up,

02:12.750 --> 02:14.150
you would want to see the general first.

02:14.150 --> 02:14.750
So...

02:14.910 --> 02:16.970
Where is the medicine I brought back?

02:17.840 --> 02:19.240
You were holding it so tightly,

02:19.240 --> 02:20.430
refusing to let go.

02:29.870 --> 02:30.910
Xiao Chi,

02:31.240 --> 02:32.960
look what I brought back.

02:34.680 --> 02:35.750
Don't worry,

02:36.960 --> 02:39.000
you will wake up soon.

03:34.280 --> 03:36.000
Why doesn't it work?

03:43.000 --> 03:44.630
Your Majesty, since we left the palace,

03:44.630 --> 03:46.240
you've kept my eyes blindfolded.

03:46.240 --> 03:48.040
Where exactly are you taking me?

03:49.079 --> 03:50.079
This is the place.

03:54.840 --> 03:56.910
This street is so beautiful at night.

03:56.910 --> 03:57.750
It's alright.

04:07.400 --> 04:08.080
But

04:08.080 --> 04:09.360
why is there no one around?

04:09.360 --> 04:11.290
I told the vendors to go home early.

04:11.840 --> 04:12.680
But

04:12.870 --> 04:14.400
I bought all their goods.

04:16.190 --> 04:18.050
Why did you do that, Your Majesty?

04:18.269 --> 04:20.399
I've always envied the common people.

04:20.950 --> 04:21.560
They

04:21.870 --> 04:23.480
can take their loved ones

04:24.040 --> 04:25.830
and stroll through the market.

04:26.680 --> 04:27.480
They can also

04:27.680 --> 04:28.950
pick out some little items

04:28.950 --> 04:30.680
handmade by the small vendors.

04:30.870 --> 04:32.200
It's very interesting.

04:32.830 --> 04:35.270
You didn't have to buy everything, though.

04:35.270 --> 04:37.430
Well, I couldn't just
chase them home.

04:39.240 --> 04:39.840
By the way,

04:40.040 --> 04:41.100
in a couple of days,

04:41.270 --> 04:43.070
the delegation from Changmo
will be arriving.

04:43.070 --> 04:44.159
You can pick

04:44.159 --> 04:46.190
some things you like here,

04:46.360 --> 04:48.360
or things you find interesting,

04:48.630 --> 04:49.750
and have them take them back.

04:49.750 --> 04:50.920
Consider it

04:51.240 --> 04:52.040
a return gift,

04:52.040 --> 04:52.560
okay?

04:52.630 --> 04:53.270
Really?

04:54.360 --> 04:56.950
Then I'll have them take it all away,

04:57.159 --> 04:58.390
and let the people of Changmo

04:58.390 --> 05:00.480
see just how bustling
these streets can be.

05:00.480 --> 05:01.120
Sure.

05:01.120 --> 05:02.430
They can take it all away.

05:02.430 --> 05:03.160
You said it.

05:03.270 --> 05:03.630
Yeah.

05:14.830 --> 05:15.480
Take this.

05:20.630 --> 05:21.510
You wear this.

05:22.160 --> 05:22.600
Yeah.

05:51.870 --> 05:52.680
Let's go.

06:11.070 --> 06:12.430
The medical hall's business is good.

06:12.430 --> 06:13.890
Any good medicinal herbs?

06:14.040 --> 06:14.870
Uncle Lie.

06:17.000 --> 06:17.800
Why are you here?

06:17.800 --> 06:18.680
You wouldn't go back to Changmo,

06:18.680 --> 06:20.680
so of course I came to see you myself.

06:20.830 --> 06:21.630
Now,

06:21.630 --> 06:23.190
the two countries have
formed a marriage alliance,

06:23.190 --> 06:24.480
and the borders have opened for trade.

06:24.480 --> 06:25.160
I came

06:25.160 --> 06:27.160
with the merchant caravan from Fengyang.

06:27.160 --> 06:28.600
For one thing, they told me

06:28.600 --> 06:30.430
there's a very good medical hall
in the north of the city,

06:30.430 --> 06:31.800
and the physician is very skilled,

06:31.800 --> 06:33.190
who seems to have cured

06:33.190 --> 06:34.240
a plague in some village.

06:34.240 --> 06:36.570
Of course I had to come
and learn from them.

06:36.870 --> 06:38.680
Uncle Lie, you're making fun of me.

06:38.680 --> 06:39.510
Not at all.

06:41.630 --> 06:43.159
I found Mo.

06:43.430 --> 06:45.680
But I settled him
in a bamboo grove cottage,

06:45.680 --> 06:46.870
and haven't brought him over yet.

06:46.870 --> 06:47.830
You found Mo?

06:47.830 --> 06:49.070
How is he doing now?

06:49.190 --> 06:51.190
He has suffered a lot over the years.

06:51.480 --> 06:53.159
He hasn't woken up yet.

06:53.390 --> 06:54.390
Thanks to Xiao Chi.

06:54.390 --> 06:55.120
Otherwise, I wouldn't have been able

06:55.120 --> 06:56.830
to save him alone.

06:58.430 --> 06:59.480
Xiao Chi?

07:00.680 --> 07:02.140
Then I should find a chance

07:02.310 --> 07:04.240
to thank him.

07:05.240 --> 07:05.830
By the way,

07:05.830 --> 07:07.680
I live in Jie'an Ward
in the south of the city.

07:07.680 --> 07:08.740
Tomorrow morning.

07:08.830 --> 07:10.390
Bring Mo over early in the morning,

07:10.390 --> 07:11.790
so I can help him recover.

07:13.600 --> 07:14.390
Great.

07:16.000 --> 07:16.870
I see you

07:16.870 --> 07:18.430
have lost a lot of weight since last time.

07:18.430 --> 07:19.920
Is something on your mind?

07:20.560 --> 07:21.310
Don't worry.

07:21.630 --> 07:22.560
With me here,

07:22.560 --> 07:24.070
anything can be solved.

07:24.830 --> 07:25.360
Mhm.

07:25.360 --> 07:27.270
I have things to do, so I'll get going.

07:27.270 --> 07:28.070
Mhm.

07:41.070 --> 07:42.159
Uncle Lie is here.

07:42.390 --> 07:44.790
He will definitely be
able to cure Xiao Chi.

08:01.160 --> 08:02.070
Come out.

08:08.800 --> 08:10.160
It's been a while, Fei Zheng.

08:10.160 --> 08:10.950
Hall Master.

08:12.360 --> 08:14.000
When did you arrive in the capital?

08:14.000 --> 08:15.600
The marriage alliance went smoothly.

08:15.600 --> 08:16.680
The borders are open.

08:16.680 --> 08:18.120
The tribute envoys coming to the capital

08:18.120 --> 08:19.580
had an unimpeded journey.

08:20.190 --> 08:22.590
Lord Fei, you deserve
some credit for this.

08:24.430 --> 08:26.630
I've done everything I was supposed to.

08:26.630 --> 08:27.830
What more do you want?

08:27.830 --> 08:30.240
You really think you've
grown strong enough

08:30.240 --> 08:32.360
to escape Changmo's control?

08:32.840 --> 08:33.870
Don't forget,

08:34.000 --> 08:36.480
you are a spy sent by Changmo to Jinglan.

08:38.080 --> 08:40.409
Now, whether it's for Changmo or Jinglan,

08:40.549 --> 08:42.720
I only hope the 2 countries
can have everlasting peace.

08:42.720 --> 08:43.669
Peace?

08:45.030 --> 08:46.080
I think you are just reluctant to give up

08:46.080 --> 08:48.240
your position
as an important court minister.

08:48.240 --> 08:49.240
Say what you will.

08:50.080 --> 08:52.410
All these years, I have a clear conscience

08:52.510 --> 08:53.550
towards Changmo.

08:55.080 --> 08:56.390
A clear conscience?

08:57.630 --> 08:58.750
What about Jin Xi?

08:59.000 --> 09:01.080
Do you have
a clear conscience towards her, too?

09:01.080 --> 09:03.480
You led her onto
the path of becoming a spy.

09:04.840 --> 09:06.480
Then please show mercy, Hall Master.

09:06.480 --> 09:07.360
Give her the antidote,

09:07.360 --> 09:08.440
spare her life,

09:08.440 --> 09:09.770
and return her freedom.

09:11.600 --> 09:13.080
She can't run away.

09:14.200 --> 09:15.330
And neither can you.

09:17.080 --> 09:19.740
What exactly are you
trying to say, Hall Master?

09:21.080 --> 09:22.080
In the Jinglan court,

09:22.080 --> 09:24.080
I need someone more obedient.

09:24.080 --> 09:25.790
Ask Li Shichang out.

09:26.000 --> 09:26.960
Otherwise,

09:26.960 --> 09:28.390
I'll let the Emperor of Jinglan

09:28.390 --> 09:30.080
know your true identity.

09:30.670 --> 09:31.630
Let's see then

09:31.630 --> 09:33.510
if he still acknowledges
you as his second brother.

09:33.510 --> 09:34.360
Meng Ling.

09:38.750 --> 09:39.550
Fine.

09:40.550 --> 09:41.880
If I agree to your terms,

09:42.600 --> 09:44.600
you must give the antidote to Jin Xi.

09:47.240 --> 09:48.200
Sure.

09:49.080 --> 09:50.280
This is the last time.

09:56.670 --> 09:57.150
Come on,

09:57.390 --> 09:58.150
Lord Li.

09:58.390 --> 09:59.190
A toast to you.

10:03.600 --> 10:05.360
You must be joking, Lord Fei.

10:05.360 --> 10:06.720
It's my honor to share a drink

10:06.720 --> 10:08.240
with one of Jinglan's finest

10:08.240 --> 10:09.670
under such

10:09.750 --> 10:11.480
a lovely night.

10:34.030 --> 10:35.150
Why is she here?

10:36.750 --> 10:37.670
Lord Fei,

10:38.440 --> 10:40.550
you seem to have a special liking

10:40.550 --> 10:42.000
for this dancer.

10:43.790 --> 10:45.550
You must be joking, Lord Li.

10:45.750 --> 10:47.240
I simply think

10:47.840 --> 10:50.480
this dancer's style is quite unique.

10:52.670 --> 10:53.320
Lord Fei,

10:53.630 --> 10:55.790
you must be joking.

10:56.390 --> 10:58.360
This dancer's performance

10:58.360 --> 10:59.870
is quite average.

11:00.630 --> 11:02.320
Even her most basic steps

11:02.670 --> 11:04.870
are not on the beat.

11:06.870 --> 11:08.440
Although her dancing

11:08.440 --> 11:10.360
is not great,

11:10.870 --> 11:12.120
fortunately,

11:12.120 --> 11:13.630
she is pretty

11:13.630 --> 11:15.200
and gentle.

11:15.440 --> 11:17.700
I seem to have seen her somewhere before.

11:33.030 --> 11:33.670
Jin Xi,

11:34.270 --> 11:35.200
it really is you.

11:35.550 --> 11:36.840
Why are you here?

11:37.480 --> 11:38.600
Lord Fei,

11:38.870 --> 11:41.400
you are still as naive
as when you were a child.

11:53.670 --> 11:54.870
You put a Gu inside me?

11:56.480 --> 11:57.270
Despicable.

11:57.270 --> 11:59.670
Those who achieve great things
don't bother about trifles.

11:59.670 --> 12:01.800
This Gu poison will act up once a month.

12:01.840 --> 12:03.480
And it feels terrible.

12:03.840 --> 12:05.670
Will you listen to me now?

12:07.670 --> 12:09.470
You must be joking, Hall Master.

12:09.670 --> 12:11.480
Of all the missions sent
from Changmo over the years,

12:11.480 --> 12:12.510
which one wasn't completed by me

12:12.510 --> 12:13.870
with hard work?

12:14.840 --> 12:16.100
I have never forgotten

12:16.440 --> 12:17.840
my oath to Changmo.

12:19.670 --> 12:21.600
If what you say is true,

12:21.870 --> 12:24.480
I will naturally give you
an antidote every month.

12:24.480 --> 12:26.200
But as for this antidote now,

12:26.200 --> 12:27.660
will you take it yourself,

12:27.870 --> 12:29.150
or give it to her?

12:30.030 --> 12:30.870
You choose.

12:40.960 --> 12:42.440
Jin Xi is nothing

12:42.840 --> 12:44.240
but a tool to me.

12:50.030 --> 12:51.670
Men are all like this.

13:00.600 --> 13:01.390
Jin Xi.

13:03.200 --> 13:04.000
Jin Xi.

13:06.150 --> 13:07.270
Has it really

13:08.120 --> 13:09.840
come to this between us?

13:36.480 --> 13:38.870
These were all sent
by the Changmo delegation?

13:38.870 --> 13:39.630
Yes.

13:40.080 --> 13:41.840
This is unique to Changmo.

13:42.240 --> 13:43.320
It's called a pomegranate.

13:43.320 --> 13:43.670
Oh.

13:43.670 --> 13:44.480
And this.

13:45.270 --> 13:46.550
This is called a fig.

13:46.550 --> 13:48.410
It looks like a mini pomegranate.

13:48.750 --> 13:49.550
And this.

13:50.030 --> 13:51.690
This is called a yellow peach.

13:51.960 --> 13:53.910
There are gold and silver,

13:53.910 --> 13:55.200
furs and fine clothes,

13:55.200 --> 13:56.800
and these specialty fruits.

13:57.080 --> 13:58.360
Seeing them

13:58.910 --> 14:00.750
is like returning to Changmo.

14:02.670 --> 14:03.510
My love.

14:04.270 --> 14:05.200
Missing home?

14:08.790 --> 14:10.960
Home is wherever you are.

14:12.600 --> 14:13.910
How about next time,

14:13.910 --> 14:16.480
we ask your father
to come with the delegation?

14:16.480 --> 14:19.140
I've always wanted to have
a good drink with him.

14:20.030 --> 14:21.560
My father is in poor health.

14:21.600 --> 14:23.730
He might not be able to travel that far.

14:24.440 --> 14:25.640
That doesn't matter.

14:26.030 --> 14:28.790
Then next time I will
accompany you back to Changmo

14:28.790 --> 14:30.050
to visit him properly.

14:36.200 --> 14:38.060
You're sleepy in broad daylight?

14:38.360 --> 14:40.760
I've been eating
and sleeping a lot lately.

14:42.270 --> 14:43.150
I was thinking,

14:44.120 --> 14:45.440
could I be

14:46.080 --> 14:47.030
pregnant?

14:49.870 --> 14:51.030
What did you say?

14:56.360 --> 14:58.960
This is great news
for Jinglan and Changmo!

15:00.360 --> 15:02.080
I will announce it to the world tomorrow

15:02.080 --> 15:04.080
and let everyone know the good news.

15:04.440 --> 15:05.790
Don't rush.

15:06.390 --> 15:07.360
It's so embarrassing.

15:07.360 --> 15:08.480
I'm not sure yet.

15:08.630 --> 15:10.750
What's there to be embarrassed about?

15:10.750 --> 15:13.000
This is the first child of you and me.

15:13.670 --> 15:15.630
Whether it's a boy or a girl,

15:15.870 --> 15:17.390
I will protect them well.

15:18.270 --> 15:19.390
I want them

15:20.030 --> 15:22.150
to come into this world safely.

15:22.360 --> 15:24.490
I will teach them how to read and write.

15:25.240 --> 15:26.790
If it's a boy,

15:27.480 --> 15:28.440
I will

15:29.390 --> 15:30.320
give him a title,

15:30.870 --> 15:32.330
let him inherit my throne,

15:33.200 --> 15:35.440
and let him govern Jinglan well.

15:36.270 --> 15:37.600
And if it's a girl?

15:39.670 --> 15:41.080
If it's a girl,

15:42.000 --> 15:43.120
we will

15:43.910 --> 15:45.600
find her a good husband,

15:46.150 --> 15:47.870
marry her off in style,

15:48.360 --> 15:49.890
and make her as happy as you.

15:51.630 --> 15:52.360
And then?

15:52.870 --> 15:53.550
Then...

15:54.510 --> 15:55.570
Then we keep going.

15:56.080 --> 15:56.870
Keep going?

15:57.550 --> 15:59.880
You thought you could
just have one or two?

15:59.960 --> 16:01.030
I will definitely make you

16:01.030 --> 16:02.030
have 10 or 20 kids

16:02.030 --> 16:02.840
before I let you go.

16:02.840 --> 16:04.200
Ten or twenty?

16:04.670 --> 16:05.550
I'm not a mouse.

16:05.550 --> 16:07.120
How could I have that many?

16:11.080 --> 16:11.750
Miss,

16:11.750 --> 16:13.200
come take a look at the fruit.

16:13.200 --> 16:14.870
All fine fruits from Changmo.

16:22.030 --> 16:24.600
It's rare to see such large pomegranates.

16:25.080 --> 16:26.870
You really know your stuff, Miss.

16:26.870 --> 16:28.470
Jinglan doesn't have these.

16:28.790 --> 16:30.650
Others don't know about them yet.

16:32.600 --> 16:33.870
Would you like a taste?

16:34.080 --> 16:35.030
No, thank you.

16:38.200 --> 16:39.730
You look like a kind person.

16:39.870 --> 16:40.630
Have a taste.

16:40.630 --> 16:41.790
I won't charge you.

16:44.240 --> 16:45.030
Yunling.

16:46.360 --> 16:47.820
I was just looking for you.

16:48.080 --> 16:48.870
Uncle Lie.

16:51.870 --> 16:52.840
These

16:53.030 --> 16:54.670
were all shipped from Changmo, right?

16:54.670 --> 16:56.390
For such fine goods from afar,

16:56.390 --> 16:58.450
you should sell them for a good price.

17:00.270 --> 17:01.550
I found a new antidote.

17:01.550 --> 17:03.210
You can take it back and try it.

17:04.000 --> 17:04.550
Really?

17:04.550 --> 17:05.000
Yes.

17:05.030 --> 17:06.000
Let's hurry back then.

17:06.000 --> 17:06.530
Let's go.

17:33.640 --> 17:36.240
This is the antidote pill
I brought back from Changmo.

17:36.240 --> 17:37.070
Give it

17:37.480 --> 17:38.640
to Xiao Chi.

17:39.680 --> 17:40.720
Jinglan's arrow poison

17:40.720 --> 17:42.070
shouldn't have changed.

17:42.070 --> 17:43.160
Rest assured.

17:43.440 --> 17:44.770
After taking this pill,

17:44.880 --> 17:46.340
he will surely get better.

17:46.400 --> 17:47.930
If even this can't cure him,

17:49.030 --> 17:49.680
I'm afraid

17:49.680 --> 17:51.200
no one in the world can.

17:54.000 --> 17:55.440
Xiao Chi

17:55.440 --> 17:56.590
not only saved you,

17:56.680 --> 17:57.880
but also saved my Mo.

17:58.790 --> 17:59.680
You know,

17:59.750 --> 18:00.400
I never

18:00.510 --> 18:02.270
want to owe anyone.

18:02.480 --> 18:03.680
Thank you, Uncle Lie.

18:03.880 --> 18:05.030
I'll go give it to him now.

18:05.030 --> 18:05.550
Go.

18:22.960 --> 18:24.440
It smells so sweet.

18:24.590 --> 18:25.200
It must be my

18:25.200 --> 18:26.070
Consort Ling.

18:26.680 --> 18:27.680
When did you wake up?

18:27.680 --> 18:28.810
I woke up a while ago.

18:29.160 --> 18:31.020
I woke up when you came in just now.

18:32.270 --> 18:33.510
I just wanted to see

18:33.830 --> 18:35.760
what kind of trick you'd play on me.

18:36.590 --> 18:38.160
What trick could I possibly play on you?

18:38.160 --> 18:39.490
I don't know about that.

18:40.030 --> 18:40.920
But I have to let you

18:40.920 --> 18:41.790
know

18:42.030 --> 18:42.890
how bad I can be.

18:51.000 --> 18:52.480
If you treat me badly,

18:52.590 --> 18:54.030
the baby and I won't let it go.

18:54.030 --> 18:55.030
Don't worry.

18:55.590 --> 18:56.850
For the rest of my life,

18:57.030 --> 18:59.270
I will treat you both very well.

19:02.680 --> 19:03.640
Look what I brought you.

19:03.640 --> 19:04.480
What is it?

19:04.880 --> 19:06.640
This is tribute from our envoy.

19:06.830 --> 19:08.880
It's called Zhuyao in Changmo.

19:09.440 --> 19:11.030
It's very rare.

19:11.480 --> 19:12.240
Try one.

19:12.880 --> 19:14.280
How could I bear to eat it?

19:14.750 --> 19:15.810
You can have it all.

19:16.200 --> 19:17.200
Listen to me.

19:17.400 --> 19:18.480
This Zhuyao

19:18.480 --> 19:19.550
is a custom among the women of Changmo.

19:19.550 --> 19:20.480
They feed them one by one

19:20.480 --> 19:22.070
to the man they love,

19:22.070 --> 19:23.480
symbolizing eternal union

19:23.480 --> 19:25.000
and the blessing of many children.

19:25.000 --> 19:26.270
You have to eat it.

19:27.480 --> 19:29.270
If you say so,

19:29.550 --> 19:31.440
I won't leave a single one for you.

19:33.350 --> 19:34.070
Then

19:34.750 --> 19:35.480
feed it to me.

20:25.000 --> 20:25.830
Xiao Chi.

20:26.070 --> 20:28.160
This is my uncle's special antidote.

20:28.270 --> 20:29.600
It can cure all poisons.

20:29.880 --> 20:31.750
You will be fine soon.

20:37.750 --> 20:38.310
Here.

21:27.640 --> 21:28.830
You'll be fine.

21:37.750 --> 21:38.880
Strategist Mo Du,

21:39.680 --> 21:41.030
what on earth are you thinking?

21:41.030 --> 21:42.350
Xiao Chi is injured now.

21:42.350 --> 21:43.590
Why did you save him?

21:45.030 --> 21:46.880
I don't like owing others.

21:47.200 --> 21:49.530
Just like when I fled
to Changmo back then,

21:49.880 --> 21:51.680
the King of Changmo did me a favor,

21:51.680 --> 21:52.680
so

21:52.680 --> 21:54.880
I would pledge my life to him.

21:56.830 --> 21:58.640
I see that now you are back in Jinglan,

21:58.640 --> 21:59.880
this vow to pledge your life

21:59.880 --> 22:01.720
is thrown out of the window.

22:05.350 --> 22:06.350
Hall Master,

22:06.350 --> 22:08.030
just mind your own business.

22:08.160 --> 22:09.960
No need to interfere with mine.

22:10.680 --> 22:13.480
You and I originally
had a division of labor.

22:13.790 --> 22:16.030
I make poison and spread it everywhere.

22:16.550 --> 22:17.480
And you,

22:17.830 --> 22:20.030
train spies and assassins.

22:20.880 --> 22:21.920
You and I

22:22.240 --> 22:24.070
stay out of each other's way.

22:25.400 --> 22:26.270
Even if

22:27.350 --> 22:29.550
you have an affair with King of Changmo,

22:30.640 --> 22:32.790
I don't need to follow your orders.

22:35.110 --> 22:36.030
Besides,

22:36.400 --> 22:37.720
I'm the one who taught you

22:37.720 --> 22:39.250
all those Gu tricks you use.

22:39.270 --> 22:41.920
Although you've devoted
yourself to those things,

22:41.920 --> 22:43.070
I've never thought

22:43.440 --> 22:45.550
much of them.

22:53.270 --> 22:54.960
Then let's wait and see.

24:01.350 --> 24:02.350
Thank you.

24:13.030 --> 24:14.590
When did you wake up?

24:14.590 --> 24:15.160
I...

24:17.590 --> 24:18.400
Just now.

24:20.400 --> 24:21.350
Have you been

24:21.550 --> 24:23.280
taking care of me all this time?

24:23.880 --> 24:24.640
Yeah.

24:28.680 --> 24:29.480
Now,

24:31.960 --> 24:34.070
I really can't repay you.

24:35.960 --> 24:37.240
You don't look well.

24:38.590 --> 24:40.120
Do you want to go in and rest?

24:43.440 --> 24:44.700
Let me feel your pulse.

24:44.830 --> 24:45.680
Come in.

24:50.350 --> 24:51.240
Your Highness.

24:51.510 --> 24:53.440
Consort Ling seems to be pregnant.

24:53.640 --> 24:54.510
Really?

24:54.680 --> 24:57.240
I heard Consort Ling
tell His Majesty herself.

24:57.240 --> 24:58.550
It shouldn't be false.

24:58.790 --> 25:01.050
This is the first child of the Liu family.

25:01.590 --> 25:03.120
Whether it's a boy or a girl,

25:03.240 --> 25:04.590
it's a joyous event.

25:05.400 --> 25:06.550
But Your Highness,

25:06.880 --> 25:08.270
I am worried...

25:10.000 --> 25:11.530
What are you worried about?

25:12.240 --> 25:13.160
Pregnancy

25:13.550 --> 25:15.160
takes 10 months.

25:16.270 --> 25:18.400
Come with me to Consort Ling's palace.

25:22.790 --> 25:23.590
What's wrong?

25:25.480 --> 25:28.030
Your Highness is fine.

25:28.640 --> 25:30.440
And the fetus...

25:30.920 --> 25:32.450
What's wrong with the baby?

25:33.880 --> 25:35.080
It's even healthier.

25:36.590 --> 25:38.720
You scared me to death, Physician Han.

25:40.550 --> 25:41.550
Physician Han.

25:41.720 --> 25:43.480
You've been taking care
of me all along the way.

25:43.480 --> 25:45.680
Now you have to take care of my child too.

25:47.160 --> 25:48.640
It's my duty as a physician.

25:48.640 --> 25:49.790
Besides,

25:49.830 --> 25:51.160
I also want to see

25:51.160 --> 25:53.690
what the lovely Princess's
child looks like.

25:55.510 --> 25:57.200
Then I also want to see

25:57.200 --> 25:58.160
what the child of the beautiful physician

25:58.160 --> 25:59.440
and the heroic general

25:59.440 --> 26:00.480
will look like.

26:00.480 --> 26:01.640
Your Highness.

26:02.270 --> 26:03.240
If you keep saying that,

26:03.240 --> 26:04.970
I won't care about you anymore.

26:07.440 --> 26:08.300
Where is Jin Xi?

26:10.110 --> 26:12.370
Princess Xie granted
Jin Xi a courtyard.

26:12.550 --> 26:14.010
She has already moved out.

26:15.200 --> 26:16.000
Wanyu.

26:16.000 --> 26:17.830
Greetings, Your Highness.

26:18.480 --> 26:19.350
Xie.

26:20.160 --> 26:21.690
Greetings, Your Highness.

26:21.830 --> 26:23.440
Dispense with the formalities.

26:23.440 --> 26:24.200
Wanyu.

26:24.720 --> 26:25.350
I...

26:25.350 --> 26:26.350
I specifically called a top gynecologist

26:26.350 --> 26:28.440
from the Imperial Medical Academy
to examine you.

26:28.440 --> 26:29.720
So I can rest assured.

26:29.960 --> 26:30.880
Thank you, Xie.

26:31.590 --> 26:32.850
This is Physician Han.

26:32.880 --> 26:34.270
I was sick all the way from Changmo,

26:34.270 --> 26:35.530
and she took care of me.

26:37.000 --> 26:38.480
With Physician Han taking care of you,

26:38.480 --> 26:39.810
I am even more relieved.

26:40.240 --> 26:41.480
I will do my best.

26:42.270 --> 26:44.160
I will take my leave now.

26:44.550 --> 26:45.200
Okay.

26:48.350 --> 26:49.550
Sit down.

26:49.550 --> 26:50.350
Sit down, Xie.

26:52.640 --> 26:55.170
Although Physician Han
is looking after you,

26:55.240 --> 26:56.480
you still need to

26:56.480 --> 26:58.790
pay close attention
to your own body at all times.

26:58.790 --> 26:59.880
Don't worry, Xie.

27:00.030 --> 27:00.790
I will.

27:00.790 --> 27:01.550
Come.

27:01.550 --> 27:02.350
Put it here.

27:03.640 --> 27:04.350
I've

27:04.350 --> 27:06.000
prepared a little gift for you.

27:06.000 --> 27:07.270
I hope you like it.

27:09.350 --> 27:10.030
This is...

27:10.240 --> 27:12.640
These are the clothes
His Majesty wore when he was a child.

27:12.640 --> 27:14.590
I've always kept them.

27:14.880 --> 27:15.790
Now

27:15.790 --> 27:17.000
they come in handy.

27:18.640 --> 27:20.270
It's so cute!

27:20.270 --> 27:22.000
I'm glad you don't mind.

27:22.070 --> 27:23.480
How could I mind?

27:23.680 --> 27:25.640
These are the clothes Liu Chu wore.

27:27.350 --> 27:28.310
Thank you, Xie.

27:28.400 --> 27:29.720
You're welcome.

27:30.310 --> 27:31.480
Let me feel it.

27:31.480 --> 27:33.400
Xie, it's still small.

27:35.640 --> 27:36.680
Lord Li.

27:37.030 --> 27:38.200
Tasting tea

27:38.200 --> 27:39.350
is like conducting oneself.

27:39.350 --> 27:40.200
A good cup of tea,

27:40.200 --> 27:41.270
from boiling and brewing

27:41.270 --> 27:43.440
to the aroma unfolding,

27:43.750 --> 27:47.640
takes time and patience.

27:47.680 --> 27:49.350
You are absolutely right, Lord Zhang.

27:49.350 --> 27:51.000
Your theory on tea

27:51.000 --> 27:53.680
has completely convinced me.

27:53.750 --> 27:55.400
Wang Ruhai

27:55.400 --> 27:57.200
doesn't understand this.

27:57.830 --> 27:58.270
Please.

27:58.270 --> 27:59.030
My Lord.

27:59.350 --> 28:00.550
Something happened.

28:01.790 --> 28:02.510
What is it?

28:02.510 --> 28:03.790
Why the panic?

28:04.240 --> 28:05.770
His Majesty has fallen ill.

28:07.200 --> 28:07.880
What?

28:07.880 --> 28:09.110
How is this possible?

28:10.880 --> 28:12.640
I am completely out of ideas.

28:12.720 --> 28:15.030
The problem is we
don't know what disease it is.

28:15.030 --> 28:16.270
So,

28:16.270 --> 28:17.310
what should we do?

28:17.880 --> 28:19.070
I can't tell.

28:29.880 --> 28:31.410
Forgive me, Your Highness.

28:32.070 --> 28:34.200
There is no need to keep useless hands.

28:34.270 --> 28:35.110
Yes.

28:37.590 --> 28:38.510
Your Highness!

28:38.510 --> 28:40.970
What disease exactly
does His Majesty have?

28:41.000 --> 28:42.000
Your Highness.

28:42.000 --> 28:43.790
His Majesty's symptoms are unheard of.

28:43.790 --> 28:44.350
We...

28:44.550 --> 28:45.880
We haven't figured it out yet.

28:45.880 --> 28:47.340
You haven't figure it out?

28:47.590 --> 28:48.510
At this point,

28:48.510 --> 28:49.880
you still don't even know the cause.

28:49.880 --> 28:51.240
What use are you?

28:54.200 --> 28:55.680
Please calm down, Your Highness.

28:55.680 --> 28:56.510
We...

28:56.880 --> 28:59.110
We really have tried our best.

28:59.110 --> 29:00.920
Indeed.

29:07.310 --> 29:09.160
Summon Fei Zheng
and Xiao Chi to the palace.

29:09.160 --> 29:10.290
Yes, Your Highness.

29:18.590 --> 29:19.350
Xiao Chi.

29:19.590 --> 29:20.880
How are you feeling?

29:21.680 --> 29:23.400
Thank you for your concern, Your Highness.

29:23.400 --> 29:24.800
I am completely fine now.

29:25.270 --> 29:26.670
How about His Majesty...

29:27.790 --> 29:29.240
What did the imperial physicians say?

29:29.240 --> 29:30.160
Those quacks

29:30.680 --> 29:32.110
say His Majesty seems ill but isn't,

29:32.110 --> 29:33.570
seems poisoned but isn't.

29:33.720 --> 29:35.830
The whole Imperial Medical Academy
is helpless.

29:35.830 --> 29:38.310
His Majesty's illness came
on very suddenly.

29:38.310 --> 29:39.830
Was His Majesty's food

29:40.590 --> 29:41.480
checked?

29:42.270 --> 29:43.680
His Majesty's daily routine

29:43.680 --> 29:45.080
is your responsibility.

29:45.200 --> 29:46.160
You tell me.

29:46.440 --> 29:47.510
Your Highness,

29:47.830 --> 29:50.270
His Majesty's daily routine
has been as usual lately.

29:50.270 --> 29:51.790
Everything His Majesty consumes

29:51.790 --> 29:53.200
is carefully examined.

29:53.270 --> 29:54.440
Only after confirming it is non-toxic

29:54.440 --> 29:56.040
do we serve it to His Majesty.

29:56.440 --> 29:57.270
However...

29:57.270 --> 29:58.070
Speak.

29:58.680 --> 30:02.270
But a batch of food offered as tribute
by the Changmo delegation earlier

30:02.270 --> 30:04.200
was sent directly to Consort Ling.

30:04.200 --> 30:06.200
Although we have checked most of it,

30:06.720 --> 30:07.830
I'm just afraid...

30:10.510 --> 30:12.240
It's related to Changmo again.

30:13.680 --> 30:14.540
Your Highness.

30:15.070 --> 30:16.920
The most important thing now is

30:16.920 --> 30:18.640
to have His Majesty wake up quickly.

30:18.640 --> 30:20.110
Once His Majesty wakes up,

30:20.110 --> 30:21.720
whether it's poison or illness,

30:21.720 --> 30:23.000
we can investigate it however we want.

30:23.000 --> 30:24.680
I wonder if Your Highness remembers

30:24.680 --> 30:26.440
the physician who rendered
great service in Huangpi Village,

30:26.440 --> 30:27.270
Han Yunling.

30:29.790 --> 30:30.920
She previously

30:30.920 --> 30:32.510
spent some time in Changmo.

30:32.920 --> 30:34.480
Perhaps having her treat
His Majesty in the palace

30:34.480 --> 30:35.940
will yield some progress.

30:36.590 --> 30:38.510
So many senior imperial physicians
are helpless.

30:38.510 --> 30:40.170
Physician Han is still young.

30:40.270 --> 30:41.680
This is no joke.

30:43.510 --> 30:44.680
Your Highness,

30:44.720 --> 30:46.880
my illness was cured by Physician Han.

30:47.070 --> 30:49.640
Besides, we have no
other options at present.

30:50.270 --> 30:51.800
Perhaps we can give it a try.

30:52.310 --> 30:54.640
I beg Your Highness
to let Han Yunling try.

31:01.590 --> 31:02.160
Granted.

31:02.310 --> 31:03.070
You may rise.

31:03.310 --> 31:04.770
Thank you, Your Highness.

31:06.240 --> 31:08.570
I don't know
when His Majesty will wake up.

31:08.880 --> 31:10.680
You two must keep things steady.

31:10.680 --> 31:12.270
We can't let the court fall into chaos.

31:12.270 --> 31:13.400
Yes, Your Highness.

31:13.720 --> 31:15.920
I will stay here
to look after His Majesty.

31:15.920 --> 31:16.550
Xiao Chi,

31:17.110 --> 31:19.000
go bring Physician Han into the palace.

31:19.000 --> 31:19.680
Fei Zheng,

31:20.270 --> 31:22.680
go investigate the cause of His Majesty's illness.

31:22.680 --> 31:23.720
I accept your command.
